{"tid":1772179,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12月8日 9:30 AM 西灣國殤紀念墳場：紀念加拿大軍保衛香港活動","createTime":"2019-12-06T11:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T12:32:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9bdb20fbc6ac6da4c02b9651c611a53830b8383","tid":1772179,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:38:56.000Z","msg":"12月8日星期日，是加拿大紀念 #香港保衛戰 儀式的日子，亦剛巧是1941年戰事爆發的同一日。儀式自1947年起已每年舉辦，歡迎公眾出席：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/514408279232258/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F514408279232258%2F&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruW5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=bbdee931\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/514408279232258/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/76175674_2924501630913218_1273188049253040128_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ohc=BHJzFcEr9fQAQl772E7eMJJsw5iZGN2VBknphmBMvxkemdAydI0lqxiaA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=9858765aacbe660ca2a23024ceb224bd&amp;oe=5E85EF25\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F76175674_2924501630913218_1273188049253040128_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ohc%3DBHJzFcEr9fQAQl772E7eMJJsw5iZGN2VBknphmBMvxkemdAydI0lqxiaA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D9858765aacbe660ca2a23024ceb224bd%26oe%3D5E85EF25&h=b61fdba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Canadian Commemorative Ceremony honours the 1,975 Canadian soldiers who bravely fought to defend Hong Kong during the Second World War and remembers the 550 who died here, in battle or captivity. Held annually at the Sai Wan War Cemetery since 1947, this important event takes place on a Sunday in early December, representing the start of hostilities in Hong Kong on December 8, 1941. It was in Hong Kong that Canadian soldiers first committed to battle in the Second World War. They were the last to come home.<br />\n<br />\nThe ceremony gives us the opportunity to honour the courage of the men and women of the Canadian Forces, both past and present, and the great sacrifices they have made in the defence of Canadian values. The ceremony is open to all and the Consulate General of Canada welcomes you to join in the commemoration."},{"pid":"30d284b881b7a3e013bc088a016bb4f007abca2d","tid":1772179,"uid":199332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"手足咁有心整嘅文宣都冇人推？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1772164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1772164</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d49ffd15a1f42da3f22ba53c48334376998c00eb","tid":1772179,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7111c484bb295e73bd38d907e5ae5411b3a3ae0e","tid":1772179,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"毋忘1941年已STAND W/ HONG KONG的加拿大友軍！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/g0qSr8WB/Candian-Forces.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fg0qSr8WB%2FCandian-Forces.jpg&h=c348e249&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52d5305f47d015eb64ff9ad9d821105ecee51a0a","tid":1772179,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"毋忘友軍！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.thestar.com/bC4fPTMlaUmlxErOo_24dQO9NfQ=/1086x738/smart/filters:cb(2700061000)/https://www.thestar.com/content/dam/thestar/news/canada/2009/12/06/harper_pays_tribute_to_fallen_soldiers_in_hong_kong/stephen_harper_in_hongkong.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.thestar.com%2FbC4fPTMlaUmlxErOo_24dQO9NfQ%3D%2F1086x738%2Fsmart%2Ffilters%3Acb%282700061000%29%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.t